com.muquit.libsodiumjna

Interface SodiumLibrary.Sodium

  • Enclosing class:
    SodiumLibrary

    public static interface SodiumLibrary.Sodium
    Declare all the supported libsodium C functions in this interface and implement them in this class as static methods.
